§ANNODRAFT[
§Two ways to do it:  1. For Hardware documentation click Add Snapshot(1), to start the camera stream. You can now position the subject and your camera until you are satisfied with how it looks. Clicking the Snapshot button (1) again will capture the last picture from the camera and stop the camera stream.  2. For documenting things presented on a computer screen, copy the screen-portion to the clipboard (Using a snipping tool is recommended) and insert it using the Insert from Clipboard button (2).                
]ANNODRAFT§
